The civil fines and penalties set forth in § 825 or in an applicable provision of this chapter, provided, however, that where a specific civil fine or penalty is not listed in § 825 or in this chapter, the fine shall be one hundred dollars ($100),
        that where a fare is charged to any person based on information entered by the operator into any device other than as required for an authorized additional charge under § 801.7 (b), the fine shall be two hundred fifty dollars ($250), and that,
        in all instances where a civil fine may be imposed, it shall double for the second violation of the same provision, and triple for each violation of the same provision thereafter;
